title: Leave the Child Alone
itunes:title: Leave the Child Alone
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see how our listeners felt after many had a lot to say once news broke about Dwayne Wade's son transitioning. Moreover, Charlamagne gave another "Donkey of the Day" to a Floridian who tried to pull over a police officer. and gets busted for a DUI. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
